# Beebs theme (Cursor)

This repo is a **Shopify Online Store 2.0** theme (Liquid, JSON templates, sections).

## Critical settings

Maintain the same facts here and in **`CLAUDE.md`** (Critical settings table) when values change.

| Setting | Your value | Notes |
|--------|------------|--------|
| Production URL | `https://beebsgoods.com/` | |
| Shopify admin store | _e.g. `the-elastic-space-of-meaning.myshopify.com`_ | |
| Live theme name or ID | _fill in_ | |
| Dev / preview theme | _fill in_ | |
| Footer column menus (handles) | Shop / About / Social → _handles_ | Navigation → Footer blocks |
| Main menu handle | _fill in_ | |
| Metaobject: reviews | `featured_review` | |
| Metaobject: stores | `store_location` | |
| Reviews page | `pages.reviews` or `/pages/reviews` | |

Do not commit secrets; document locations only.

## Agent guardrails

- Prefer **existing section patterns** before adding new global settings.
- **Never** add multiple `link_list` fields to the **root** `settings` of one section.
- Be cautious re-adding **`@app`** to sections that already use multiple resource pickers (e.g. several menus in blocks); validate with `shopify theme check` / upload before assuming schema is valid.
- Match existing Liquid/CSS naming and file layout; avoid unrelated refactors.
- If a change is a bad idea, please push back on it.

## Commands

`shopify theme dev` · `shopify theme deploy`
